'''[[Andra (Telos IV)|Andra's]] residence''' was a structure in the capital city of [[Thani]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Telos IV]]. One of the building's entrances was built into a water tower facade on the roof of the building. Andra led the operations of the [[Preserve Our Wild Endangered Resources Party|POWER party]] in the residence.

